definitions.definition: Of or pertaining to a conchoid ; that may be defined as a conchoid.
Irregular , with planar , concentric curves, similar to those on a mussel shell.
That fractures with planar concentric curves (e.g., as flint , chert or obsidian ).

main_definition: ( mathematics ) Of or pertaining to a conchoid ; that may be defined as a conchoid.
